  "text": "Cell Culture MCF-7 cells (tamoxifen-sensitive, ER-positive human breast cancer cell line) were purchased from the American Type Culture Collection. MCF-7-LCC2 cells (tamoxifenresistant, ER-positive breast cancer cell line) were kindly provided by Robert Clark [CITATION_1] . MCF-7 and MCF-7-LCC2 cells were cultured as described previously [CITATION_2] .",
